			<CASNumber>CID 24816</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Silicon tetrachloride or tetrachlorosilane is the inorganic compound with the formula SiCl4. It is a colorless volatile liquid that fumes in air. It is used to produce high purity silicon and silica for commercial applications. It is a part of the chlorosilane family. It can react with water violently and forms white solid silicon dioxide and HCl gas. It is soluble in water. It is decomposed by water to hydrochloric acid with evolution of heat. It is corrosive to metals and tissue in the presence of moisture. It is used in smoke screens, to make various silicon containing chemicals, and in chemical analysis.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">四氯化硅或四氯硅烷是一种无机化合物，化学式为 SiCl4。它是一种在空气中发烟的无色挥发性液体。它用于生产商业用途的高纯度硅和二氧化硅。它属于氯硅烷家族。它能与水发生剧烈反应，生成白色固体二氧化硅和 HCl 气体。它可溶于水。它遇水分解为盐酸，并产生热量。遇湿对金属和组织有腐蚀性。它可用于烟幕、制造各种含硅化学品和化学分析。</common:generalComment>
